---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="Somatic Services | Mikey Somatics">

  <!-- Hero -->
  <section class="py-12 bg-sand">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-6 text-center">
      <p class="text-sm tracking-widest uppercase text-sage mb-3">Services</p>
      <h1 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-light text-forest mb-4">Somatic Trauma Packages</h1>
      <p class="text-charcoal/70 leading-relaxed max-w-2xl mx-auto">
        Together, we'll gently expand the edges of your comfort zone, helping you feel more balanced and able to navigate challenges without feeling overwhelmed or shutting down.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Pricing -->
  <section class="py-24" style="background: linear-gradient(to bottom, var(--color-sand), var(--color-cream) 20%, var(--color-cream) 80%, var(--color-sand));">
    <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-6">
      <h2 class="text-3xl font-light text-forest mb-16 text-center">Packages</h2>
      <div class="grid sm:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-4 gap-6">

        <!-- Foundations -->
        <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl p-8 shadow-sm hover:shadow-lg hover:-translate-y-2 transition-all duration-300 cursor-pointer border-2 border-forest flex flex-col">
          <h3 class="text-forest font-semibold text-lg mb-2">Foundations Package</h3>
          <p class="text-3xl font-light text-forest mb-1">$895</p>
          <p class="text-sm text-charcoal/50 mb-6">one time</p>
          <ul class="space-y-3 text-sm text-charcoal/70 mb-8 flex-1">
            <li>5 private 60-minute sessions ($179/session)</li>
            <li>Space to slow down, build awareness, and begin listening to what your body is holding.</li>
          </ul>
          <a href="/contact" class="block text-center bg-forest text-white px-6 py-3 rounded-full text-sm hover:bg-forest-light transition-colors">
            Get Started
          </a>
        </div>

        <!-- Standard -->
        <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl p-8 shadow-sm hover:shadow-lg hover:-translate-y-2 transition-all duration-300 cursor-pointer border-2 border-forest flex flex-col">
          <p class="text-xs tracking-wider uppercase text-sage mb-2">Most Popular</p>
          <h3 class="text-forest font-semibold text-lg mb-2">Standard Package</h3>
          <p class="text-3xl font-light text-forest mb-1">$1,360</p>
          <p class="text-sm text-charcoal/50 mb-6">$680.00 for 2 months</p>
          <ul class="space-y-3 text-sm text-charcoal/70 mb-8 flex-1">
            <li>8 private 60-minute sessions ($170/session)</li>
            <li>More room to go deeper after building your foundation, with a personalized plan for mapping and shifting patterns between sessions.</li>
          </ul>
          <a href="/contact" class="block text-center bg-forest text-white px-6 py-3 rounded-full text-sm hover:bg-forest-light transition-colors">
            Get Started
          </a>
        </div>

        <!-- Comprehensive -->
        <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl p-8 shadow-sm hover:shadow-lg hover:-translate-y-2 transition-all duration-300 cursor-pointer border-2 border-forest flex flex-col">
          <h3 class="text-forest font-semibold text-lg mb-2">Comprehensive Intensive</h3>
          <p class="text-3xl font-light text-forest mb-1">$1,980</p>
          <p class="text-sm text-charcoal/50 mb-6">$990.00 for 2 months</p>
          <ul class="space-y-3 text-sm text-charcoal/70 mb-8 flex-1">
            <li>12 private 60-minute sessions ($165/session)</li>
            <li>Enough trust to go into harder material, work with the body more directly, and address layered patterns that shorter containers can't reach.</li>
          </ul>
          <a href="/contact" class="block text-center bg-forest text-white px-6 py-3 rounded-full text-sm hover:bg-forest-light transition-colors">
            Get Started
          </a>
        </div>

        <!-- Single -->
        <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl p-8 shadow-sm hover:shadow-lg hover:-translate-y-2 transition-all duration-300 cursor-pointer border-2 border-forest flex flex-col">
          <h3 class="text-forest font-semibold text-lg mb-2">Single Session</h3>
          <p class="text-3xl font-light text-forest mb-1">$200</p>
          <p class="text-sm text-charcoal/50 mb-6">one time</p>
          <ul class="space-y-3 text-sm text-charcoal/70 mb-8 flex-1">
            <li>1 private 60-minute somatic session</li>
            <li>Start with one session to experience the work and see if it feels right for you.</li>
          </ul>
          <a href="/contact" class="block text-center bg-forest text-white px-6 py-3 rounded-full text-sm hover:bg-forest-light transition-colors">
            Get Started
          </a>
        </div>

      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- What to Expect -->
  <section class="py-16 bg-sand">
    <div class="max-w-5xl mx-auto px-6 grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-12 items-center">
      <div>
        <img src="/images/services-hero.png" alt="Somatic therapy session" class="rounded-2xl shadow-lg w-full saturate-[0.4]" />
      </div>
      <div>
        <p class="text-sm tracking-widest uppercase text-sage mb-3">Somatic Work</p>
        <h2 class="text-3xl font-light text-forest mb-6">What to Expect</h2>
        <div class="space-y-4 text-charcoal/70 leading-relaxed">
          <p>
            <span class="text-forest font-semibold">Free consultation.</span> A virtual conversation to understand what brought you here and see if working together feels right.
          </p>
          <p>
            <span class="text-forest font-semibold">First session.</span> Grounding practices to help you feel safe, followed by mapping what's showing up in your body.
          </p>
          <p>
            <span class="text-forest font-semibold">Ongoing work.</span> Each session builds on the last. We explore stored sensations and emotions at a pace that always feels right for you.
          </p>
          <p>
            <span class="text-forest font-semibold">Integration.</span> We close each session grounded and connected. Over time, you'll notice real shifts in how your body responds to stress.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

</Layout>